generator = EmpiricalBayesThompsonSampler(min_weight=0.0)
generator.fit(Xs=self.Xs, Ys=self.Ys, Yvars=self.Yvars, parameter_values=
    self.parameter_values, outcome_names=self.outcome_names)
arms, weights, _ = generator.gen(n=5, parameter_values=self.
    parameter_values, objective_weights=np.array([1, 0]))
self.assertEqual(arms, [[4, 4], [3, 3], [2, 2], [1, 1]])
for weight, expected_weight in zip(weights, [0.66, 0.25, 0.07, 0.02]):
    self.assertAlmostEqual(weight, expected_weight, 1)
